<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/complete-fix.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/school_header') %>
        <main>
            <section class="principal-hero-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <h1>Principal's Message</h1>
                    <p>Guiding our students towards a future of excellence and integrity.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="principal-message-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="principal-card">
                        <img src="/images/principal-placeholder.svg" alt="Principal's Image" class="principal-image">
                        <div class="principal-details">
                            <h2>Smt. Radha Sharma</h2>
                            <h3>Principal, N.R.K. Public School</h3>
                            <p>Dear Students, Parents, and Guardians,</p>
                            <p>It is with immense pleasure and a deep sense of responsibility that I welcome you to
                                N.R.K. Public School, a nurturing ground for young minds and future leaders. As the
                                Principal, I am committed to upholding our school's vision of providing quality
                                education that not only imparts knowledge but also builds character, instills values,
                                and inspires a lifelong love for learning.</p>
                            <p>In our school, every child is valued and encouraged to explore their potential, both
                                inside and outside the classroom. We believe in a holistic approach to education, where
                                academic rigor is balanced with co-curricular activities, sports, and community
                                engagement. Our dedicated team of experienced educators strives to create a safe,
                                inclusive, and stimulating environment where every student feels empowered to excel.</p>
                            <p>We understand the aspirations of parents in rural areas for their children's education,
                                and we are here to support you in every step. We encourage open communication and a
                                strong partnership between home and school, as together we can lay a strong foundation
                                for your child's success.</p>
                            <p>I invite you to join us in this exciting journey of learning and growth. Let us work hand
                                in hand to shape responsible citizens who will contribute positively to our nation.</p>
                            <p>With warm regards,<br>Smt. Radha Sharma<br>Principal, N.R.K. Public School</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="call-to-action">
                <div class="container">
                    <h2>Ready to Enroll Your Child?</h2>
                    <p>Discover how N.R.K. Public School can make a difference in your child's future.</p>
                    <a href="/school/admissions" class="cta-button primary">Explore Admissions</a>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>